lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods needed only a day to return to form after a five-week layoff. Woods had an eagle and seven birdies yesterday to move to two shots off the lead at the HSBC Champions tournament in Shanghai. After an opening-day 72, Woods closed to two shots behind Jyoti Randhawa and one behind Retief Goosen.
